### OBP Integration Testing File  
### UPDATED URLS - Make sure you have completed OAuth first: http://localhost:3000/api/bank/oauth/start

### Step 1: Test OBP Connection
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bank/sync/test
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "tokenId": 1
}

### Step 2: Sync Accounts from OBP
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bank/sync/accounts  
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "tokenId": 1
}

### Step 3: Sync Transactions for Account (replace accountId with real ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bank/sync/transactions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "limit": 20
}

### Step 4: Sync All Data (accounts + transactions)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bank/sync/all
Content-Type: application/json  
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "transactionLimit": 50
}

### Helper: Get your JWT token (login first)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-email@example.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### Helper: Check your bank tokens
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bank/tokens
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Helper: Check your accounts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Helper: Check your transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN 